      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NIKKI'S REGRET (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Last start finished 4th over 380m at this track beaten 6 lengths (22.26) behind Moustache Mick in a Grade 5 on May 19. Can find winning form. SMOKING ACE (4) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at this track over 380m behind Aston Elijah (22.49) in a P5. Leading chance. FEDERAL ARLO (5) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (22.38) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Should be about the money. HARA'S REX (8) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
